A(k,n) = \binom{n}{k} \left( \frac{k}{n} \right)^{2k} \left( \frac{n-k}{n} \right)^{2(n-k)}.
\frac{A(k,n)}{A(k-1,n)} = \frac{n-k+1}{k} \frac{k^{2k}}{(k-1)^{2k-2}} \frac{(n-k)^{2(n-k)}}{(n-k+1)^{2n-2k+2}}
=\frac{k^{2k-1}}{(k-1)^{2k-2}} \frac{(n-k)^{2n-2k}}{(n-k+1)^{2n-2k+1}} = \frac{k}{n-k} \frac{(1+1/(k-1))^{2k-2}}{(1+1/(n-k))^{2n-2k}}
\approx \frac{k}{n-k} \frac{e^2}{e^2} = \frac{k}{n-k} < 1
